disclosure is essential to the investigation.</font></code><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">
		</font></code><br><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">(c) An agency licensed under this Act or its agents shall not transfer,
