</font></code><br><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">(1) Submission of false information either on </font></code></div></td></tr><tr><td><table align="center" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td width="1"><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></code></td><td><div align="justify"><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">Department licensure forms or during an inspection;</font></code></div></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><div align="justify"><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">
</font></code><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">(2) Refusal to allow an inspection to occur;</font></code><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">
